# AI Planning System

Physics-guided artificial intelligence models simulate therapy outcomes.

Functions:

- tissue modeling
- energy propagation modeling
- safety validation
- treatment planning

---

# Therapy System

Primary energy delivery modality:

High Intensity Focused Ultrasound (HIFU)

Specifications:

Frequency: 0.5 – 3 MHz  
Adaptive amplitude control  
MR-guided therapy

